title: Manhunt 1 OST
description:
Complete Manhunt 1 game soundtrack.




- This torrent includes all of the tracks with all of the moods from the game.

- The moods were classified as green, yellow, orange and red where green is for exploration and red is for total combat.

- The soundtracks were ripped from the game archives directly by me and have been converted to MP3 128 kbps for smaller size and good quality.




RIPPING THESE TRACKS IN PARTICULAR WAS A LONG AND MENTALLY PAINFUL PROCESS, I HOPE NO ONE HAS TO DO SUCH A THING SO I SHARE IT HERE. IF YOU LIKE THESE TRACKS - PLEASE DO SEED! TNX :)
